narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Czech is a good language for those who are unsure about their language skills and are looking to learn a language while having fun too.
This class is a great language to take from the beginning! You will learn so much and not be too stressed, and you will have the wonderful privilege of getting to know Professor von Kunes!
